Privacy Policy
When you download and launch 99 Bricks Wizard Academy, we gather information about you for game design purposes.
We use GameAnalytics for this. You can read more on how GameAnalytics handles your data here:
http://www.gameanalytics.com/privacy.html
If you have any questions or comments, you can mail us directly at
